snippet: Call it a win for the system and the subs. Tony Parker, Tim Duncan and Manu Ginobili sat out with injuries as the San Antonio Spurs won handily in Chicago.
abstract: NBA Roundup; San Antonio Spurs beat Chicago Bulls, 103-89; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Call it a win for the system and the subs. Tony Parker, Tim Duncan and Manu Ginobili sat out with injuries as the San Antonio Spurs won handily in Chicago.

headline.seo: Without Tim Duncan, Tony Parker and Manu Ginobili, Spurs Beat Bulls
headline.main: Missing Three Stars, Spurs Win Anyway
